title: Claude Monet Water Lilies Eyeglass Case with Cloth
description:
Eyeglass Case developed from Claude Monet’s Water Lilies, 1906, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

Keep it close or carry it with you; our hard shell eyeglass case is the perfect accessory. Matching microfiber lens cloth included. 

  • Dimensions: Glass Case: 6.25 x 2.25 x 1.25 in. Cloth: 6 x7 in.
  • Materials: Plastic, microfiber.
